    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel <strong>half</strong> your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>into a pile of ribbons</p><p>Top, tail and grate the <strong>remaining carrot</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1637061448260-x200.jpg",
