    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into a shallow bowl and beat lightly with a fork</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> to a plate and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637061452280-x200.jpg",
