        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Coat the <strong>basa fillet</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off the excess, then add to the <strong>beaten egg</strong> and finally press into the <strong>panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over</p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
