    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spoon the <strong>katsu sauce</strong> onto the plate and serve the <strong>breaded basa</strong> over the sauce with the <strong>cooked rice</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
